    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Material comprising the skin of an unborn, prematurely born, or aborted animal, especially a calf, having very fine fibers and used for high-grade parchment and suede.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
